        <mxCell id="G4cJtlao1i6TVZgc5M13-14" parent="G4cJtlao1i6TVZgc5M13-13" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;b&gt;surface_patient_information&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Parameters&lt;/b&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;- sample_response (str)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Returns&lt;/b&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;- conversation_log (DataFrame)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;- symptom_log (DataFrame)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;- article_log (DataFrame)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;- umls_log (DataFrame)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Logic: &lt;/b&gt;Generates user_id and initializes dialogue_turn to 1. MTS_dialogue used flag and text intialized to 0 and empty string. Initial question posed: &quot;How are you feeling today?&quot; and user or sample response is read in.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="230" width="170" x="10" y="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
